Last but not least; Introducing artistic director and choreographer Nikki de Graaf.

@nikkidegraaf graduated with a first class honors degree at the @northern_school of Contemporary Dance in 2014. After her graduation she danced with the young company of Jasmin Vardimon (JV2). When she moved back to the Netherlands she invested more in her choreographic skills and in 2016 she premiered "Open" Call. Nikki has a passion for dance and especially for making dance. She wants to make a difference in the (dance) world. Not only with her work but also as a person.  We did a little interview! Get to know Nikki on www.nikkidegraafcompany.com/nikkidegraaf .
